<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, minimum-scale=1.0, maximum-scale=1.0, user-scalable=no">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="renderer" content="webkit">
    <title>项目介绍</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weixin/Public/Common/css/common/basic.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weixin/Public/Common/css/Swiper/swiper.min.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/weixin/Public/Member/css/pro.css">
    <script>
    document.getElementsByTagName('html')[0].style.fontSize = document.documentElement.clientWidth/12 + 'px';
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <article id="art" class="art">
        <section class="unit">
            <p>为不断提升基层医生的医疗技术水平，缩小不同地区和不同医院之间的临床与实践差异，提高医疗服务质量、提升在临床诊疗方面的专业技能，最终解决老百姓看病难看病贵的问题，实现“大病不出县，小病不出村”。2017年1月8日中国医疗保健国际交流促进会、北京远程光明公益基金会、首都医科大学附属北京同仁医院共同发起的     千县万医培训工程”在国家会议中心进行启动仪式。 届时启动“千县万医”线上学院。</p>
            <p>“千县万医培训工程”整合全国范围内的医疗专家资源，致力于提升我国基层医生整体医疗水平；搭建多元化的学术交流与共享平台；打造知名专家品牌；体现了重要的学术价值与社会价值。</p>
        </section>
        <section class="unit">
            <ul class="box">
                <li><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic1.jpg" width="100%" /></li>
                <li><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic2.jpg" width="100%" /></li>
                <li><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic3.jpg" width="100%" /></li>
            </ul>
        </section>
    </article>
    <section id="mask" class="mask center">
        <div class="swiper-container">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
                <div class="swiper-slide text-center"><div class="swiper-zoom-container"><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic1.jpg" width="80%" /></div></div>
                <div class="swiper-slide text-center"><div class="swiper-zoom-container"><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic2.jpg" width="80%" /></div></div>
                <div class="swiper-slide text-center"><div class="swiper-zoom-container"><img src="/weixin/Public/Member/images/pro/pic3.jpg" width="80%" /></div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
            <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
            <i></i>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
<script src="/weixin/Public/Common/js/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/weixin/Public/Common/js/swiper.js"></script>
<script>        
  var mySwiper = new Swiper('.swiper-container',{
        // 如果需要前进后退按钮
        nextButton: '.swiper-button-next',
        prevButton: '.swiper-button-prev',
        zoom: true
  });
    
    $('.unit li').click(function(){
        var index = $(this).index();
        $('#mask').addClass('active');
        mySwiper.slideTo(index, 1, false);
    });
    
    $('#mask i').click(function(){
        $('#mask').removeClass('active');
    })
</script>
</html>